|}{{#ifeq:{{{subobjects|yes}}}|yes|
{{Category/subobjects | category={{{category|}}} | page={{{page|{{FULLPAGENAME}}}}} }}|}}</includeonly><noinclude>
Closes a SemanticSchemas category display wikitable opened by
`Category/table-header`. Emits the optional backlinks section, closes
the `{|` frame, and optionally appends the subobjects block.

Parameters:
* category        - The category name. Required.
* page            - Target page for the subobjects lookup. Defaults to
                    {{FULLPAGENAME}}.
* backlinks       - "no" to suppress the backlinks row. Defaults to
                    `{{{subobjects|yes}}}` for back-compat.
* subobjects      - "no" to suppress the nested Category/subobjects
                    block (auto-generated dispatchers set this because
                    they emit inline subobject sections).
* backlink_section - Pre-baked backlinks wikitext. When set, used in
                    place of the dynamic Category/render-reverse
                    lookup.
</noinclude>
